Package: tm.plugin.dc
Version: 0.2-1
Date: 2012-03-06
Title: Text Mining Distributed Corpus Plug-In
Description: A plug-in for the text mining framework tm to support text mining 
             in a distributed way. The package provides a convinient interface for
             handling distributed corpus objects based on distributed list objects.
Authors@R: c(person("Ingo", "Feinerer", role = "aut"), person("Stefan", "Theussl", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "Stefan.Theussl@wu.ac.at"))
License: GPL-3
Depends: DSL, tm (>= 0.5-6.10)
Imports: slam (>= 0.1-22)
